rnbd-tool (1.0.9) jessie stretch buster; urgency=medium

  * command line: improve help messages on path operations
  * rnbd: a path within a session can not be designated by hca and port
  * debian: Drop unneeded dependencies patch and lsb-base
  * rnbd: smart recover which works on device, session, or path
  * rnbd: implement recover device
  * manual: update rnbd man page for session recover
  * manual: add entries for path and session recover commands
  * rnbd: implement client path recover
  * rnbd: implement client session recover
  * bash-completion: add recover command

